# arch-decision вҖ” Formal Quint FPF validation of an existing PRD

This skill is **step 2** of the NONoise architectural workflow. It applies the **First Principles Framework (Quint FPF)** вҖ” fully documented in the sibling skill \`quint-fpf\` вҖ” to a narrative PRD already written by \`arch-brainstorm\`, producing a reliability audit and updating the PRD lifecycle state.

## Position in the workflow

\`\`\`
